import { AppContext } from "../../App"; import { useContext } from "react"; export const Temp = () => { const { image, cityHumidity, cityPressure, feelsLike, cityWind, cityTemp,cityWeather } = useContext(AppContext); return (

{Math.floor(cityTemp) + " C" || ""}

{cityHumidity + " RH" || ""}

{cityPressure + " mB"}

{Math.floor(feelsLike) + " C" || ""}

{cityWind + " km/h" || ""}

{cityWeather + "" || ""}

); };
